data.description: NEW IMPROVED PRICE!    OVER $40,000 of Builder UPGRADES, too many to list!     New Construction home prices in this development are steadily increasing.  Don't miss this ''almost'' new home! Come see this stunning Ranch home located in the highly desired Del Webb Community of Carolina Gardens.This Contour model is bright, airy. The Master Suite has a  Luxurious Bathroom with a granite counters, Double Vanity, and roomy Walk-In Closet. This home also has a multifunctional FLEX space. Other upgrades include a Gourmet Kitchen, Granite Counters, Upgraded Light Switches & Outlets, Wired for Surround Sound System, Under Cabinet Lighting, screened in porch, large grilling pad and LVP flooring! Do you like extra storage? This home has an easily accessible walk up storage area. This Del Webb Active Adult Community has activities galore and a wide range of Clubs & activities to participate in.The Amenities Center boasts a large indoor pool overlooking the lake, an outdoor pool, gym, pickleball, tennis, bocci, walking trails, and gathering area with kitchen.  The monthly HOA fee includes all landscaping and lawn care, Spectrum High Speed Internet & Cable, and total access to all neighborhood amenities!.      *2-10 HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED IF YOU USE PREFERRED LENDER
